org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan

Class PartialRowKeyScanAssembler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.scan.PartialRowKeyScanAssembler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PartialRowKey, RowKeyScanAssembler

    public class PartialRowKeyScanAssembler
extends java.lang.Object
implements RowKeyScanAssembler, PartialRowKey
    Assembles a composite partial row (start/stop) key pair where each field within the composite start and stop row keys are constructed based a set of query predicates.
    Since:
    0.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    DataGraphMapping, TableMapping, UserDefinedField, PredefinedField, PreDefinedFieldName
